    • checkSlot

      public boolean checkSlot(Building newBuilding, boolean flag)
      Check if the new building can be placed in the slot
      Parameters:
      newBuilding - the building that you want to add to the city
      flag - true if the building is being added to side1, false if it's being added to side2
      Returns:
      The method returns a boolean value. If the method returns true, then the building can be placed. If the method returns false, then the building cannot be placed.
